item.title: To 31.12.2019
item.description: New update points between 01.01.2019 - 31.12.2019. The following features & hotfixes have been enhanced and corrected for you this year. New Features Version 160CU May 2019 Innovations version 160CU July 2019 Innovations version 160CU August 2019 Changes version 160CU September 2019 New features version 160CU December 2019 This is only information about enhancements & optimizations from 2019. You can find our current enhancements on the current year’s page.

item.title: To 31.12.2018
item.description: Older updates until 31.12.2018 The following Connector NAV versions are no longer supported and have been discontinued: Version < 00.125CU as of 12/31/2019 Version <00.125 as of 12/31/2018 Version <00.30 as of 12/31/2017 Version <00.05 as of 12/31/2016 Version <5.90 as of 12/31/2014 Version <5.55 as of 12/31/2013 In the following section you will find an overview of the respective innovations in a version: Innovations Version x.xx.160 Changes version 7.
